Title: Continued Waygate Exploration
Description:
<The explorer-in-training hands you a taut, rolled note. Upon investigating, it appears to be from an old friend, Thaelin Darkanvil, seeking your aid.

Before scurrying off, the critter extends its hand as if it were seeking a treat. Moments later, a loud screech rings out as the curious creature storms off empty handed.>
ObjectivesText: Meet Thaelin Darkanvil at the Rubyscale Outpost in The Waking Shores.
